Delek Real Estate Bondholders Reach Agreement on Payments

-- B y   S u s a n   L e r n e r
-- 
2011-09-26T08:32:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/delek-real-estate-bondholders-reach-agreement-on-payments.html
Delek Real Estate Ltd. (DLKR)  said its
controlling shareholders signed a memorandum of understanding
with holders of the companyâ€™s Series Dalet, Heh and Kaf-Heh
bonds.  The deal includes a one-time payment of 13 million shekels
to Kaf-Heh bondholders in exchange for agreeing to delay
principal payments until Jan. 31, 2012, according to a statement
filed today with the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange. Also, the
controlling shareholders will make an offer to buy all bonds
outstanding in July 2012, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
